# Scytale Design System

## UI Components
- Use **shadcn/ui** exclusively — never build custom UI components
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional class merging

## Fonts
- **Primary font**: `Montserrat` (`font-sans`) — use for ALL text by default
- **Display font**: `Clash Display` (`font-display`) — NEVER use unless the user explicitly requests it. Always confirm with the user before applying.

## Colors (Tailwind classes only)
- **CTA / Primary**: `bg-primary` / `text-primary` → `#6162F5`
- **Primary text**: `text-foreground` → `#3E3E3E`
- **Secondary text**: `text-muted-foreground` → `#737373`
- **Icons (default)**: `text-gray-600`
- Use only Tailwind's built-in color palette for additional colors
- Never use arbitrary hex values in classes — all custom colors are mapped to CSS variables

## Sidebar Menu
- Icon container: 20×20px (`w-5 h-5`), icon artwork 15×15px
- Icon color: `text-gray-600` (normal state)
- Text: `font-normal` (regular weight, 14px)
- Text color: `text-sidebar-foreground`
- Hover: text color change only — no background highlight
- Active item: `text-primary` with `bg-accent` background

## Examples

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
<h1 className="font-display">Title</h1>
<p className="text-[#3E3E3E]">Text</p>
<SidebarMenuButton className="font-medium">Item</SidebarMenuButton>

// ✅ GOOD
<h1 className="text-foreground font-semibold">Title</h1>
<p className="text-foreground">Text</p>
<SidebarMenuButton className="font-normal text-sidebar-foreground">Item</SidebarMenuButton>
```
